Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.19,0:04:12.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Quella nave ce l'aveva data Kaya!{Cora}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.52,0:04:14.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Aspettate! Riesco ancora a vederla!{angy}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:16.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,È la Going Merry!{angy}
