Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:22.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Q-Quell'uomo...{angy}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.23,0:05:32.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Quell'uomo è...{angy}
