Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.52,0:06:52.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,È solo un passatempo.{Cora}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.85,0:06:56.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eh...?! Non prenderci in giro!{angy}
