Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.85,0:18:07.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Quel moccioso ha i poteri \Ndi un Frutto del Diavolo?{Cora}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.48,0:18:09.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Tu– - gli inglesi vanno di you bast-, ma onestamente se si può evitare meglio-angy}Malede–{Cora}{non sono d'accordo -angy}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.57,0:18:14.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Sei un compagno del giovane spadaccino?{angy}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.11,0:18:16.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Sei stato bravo a rimanere a osservare.{Cora}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.33,0:18:24.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Tranquillo. L'ho lasciato vivere.{angy}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.96,0:18:25.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eh?{angy}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.71,0:18:28.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Fratello! Fratello! Rispondimi!{angy}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.46,0:18:29.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Zoro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.34,0:18:32.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.34,0:18:34.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ehi, veloci, fatelo salire sulla barca!{Cora}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.14,0:18:37.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sono medicine! Versategliele addosso!{letterale -angy}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.31,0:18:40.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,È troppo presto per te per morire.{Cora}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.22,0:18:43.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Il mio nome è Dracule Mihawk!{angy}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.85,0:18:45.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Conosci te stesso!{angy}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.23,0:18:46.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Conosci il mondo!{angy}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.52,0:18:47.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Diventa forte!{angy}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.81,0:18:50.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Non importa per quanti anni,{angy}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.36,0:18:52.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}ti aspetterò seduto sul trono del più forte!{Cora}{...}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.36,0:18:55.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Prova a superare questa spada!{angy}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.53,0:18:59.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Prova a superare {\i1}me{\i0}, Roronoa Zoro!{La frase è un po' più lunga, sarei interessato a sapere come sarebbe letteralmente per curiosità -Cora}{"kono ore wo"="questo me [+particella] "koete miro!"="prova a superare". Fa solo più pausee -angy}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.37,0:19:04.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Fratello! Fratello, rispondimi!{angy}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.62,0:19:04.12,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,Fratello!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.92,0:19:08.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Riuscire a far dire a Mihawk queste parole...{Cora}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.88,0:19:12.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The wording should match 07:43}Moccioso, qual è il tuo obiettivo?{angy}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.92,0:19:14.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Re dei Pirati! - angy}Il Re dei Pirati!{Cora}{maiuscola la I di "il" -angy}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.76,0:19:18.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,È una strada più ardua del superarmi.{angy}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.76,0:19:21.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Chissà, ho appena iniziato.{angy}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.60,0:19:24.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,È vivo!{angy}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.60,0:19:25.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ha solo perso i sensi!{angy}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.02,0:19:29.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Fratello! Rispondimi!{angy}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.98,0:19:27.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Fratello!{angy}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.82,0:19:30.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Zoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.57,0:19:32.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Fratello!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.24,0:19:35.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,L-Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.36,0:19:37.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,mi senti?{Cora}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.61,0:19:39.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sì!{angy}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.08,0:19:42.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ti ho fatto preoccupare?{angy}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.25,0:19:44.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sarebbe...{angy}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.33,0:19:51.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}un problema se non diventassi il \Nmiglior spadaccino del mondo, giusto?{Cora}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.17,0:19:55.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Fratello! Ti prego, non parlare più!{angy}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.05,0:19:55.13,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,Fratello!{angy}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.59,0:19:57.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Io...{angy}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.47,0:19:59.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Io non...{PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.55,0:20:02.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,non perderò mai più!{angy}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.52,0:20:09.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Fino al giorno in cui lo sconfiggerò \Ne diventerò un grande spadaccino...{Cora}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.81,0:20:11.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Non...{Cora}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.27,0:20:12.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,perderò mai più!{angy}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.32,0:20:15.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Qualche problema,{angy}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.65,0:20:18.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Re dei Pirati?!{angy}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.41,0:20:23.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,No!{nessuno!-angy}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.41,0:20:25.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Siete un bel team. - angy}Siete una bella squadra.{Cora}{dice team però (messed up english) -angy}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.20,0:20:28.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Voglio incontrarvi ancora.{angy}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.12,0:20:31.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ehi, Occhi di Falco!{angy}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.67,0:20:35.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Non eri venuto a prenderti la mia testa?{angy}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.17,0:20:38.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,La testa del conquistatore dell'East Blue, Don Krieg?{Evo}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.13,0:20:43.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Era mia intenzione,\N ma mi sono divertito abbastanza.{angy}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.05,0:20:45.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Torno a casa a dormire.{angy}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.06,0:20:48.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Potrebbe essere abbastanza per te, ma io ho ancora molte energie.{Cora}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.77,0:20:50.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,D-Don?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.27,0:20:52.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Perché sta cercando di trattenerlo qui?{Cora}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.28,0:20:57.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Muori prima di andartene!{angy}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.40,0:21:00.66,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{\t(1317,0,1,\c&HF3F4F2&\3c&HF3F4F2&\4c&HF3F4F2&)}Come immaginavo, non impara mai...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.66,0:21:10.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Tsk, è scappato.{Cora}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.55,0:21:21.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.22,0:21:22.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.59,0:21:24.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vai! Lascio Nami a te!{angy}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.43,0:21:26.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Capito!{angy}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.43,0:21:29.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Io e Zoro riporteremo indietro Nami di sicuro!{angy}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.35,0:21:31.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Tu assicurati di far diventare il cuoco nostro compagno!  - - un po' troppo lunga-angy}{/q2]Tu assicurati di far unire il cuoco alla ciurma!Cora}{sì avevo detto un po' lunga, ma come nei primi episodi, non dicono mai ciurma sostanzialmente, almeno non per ora. Sempre nakama, compagno}Tu assicurati di far diventare il cuoco un nostro compagno!{Cora}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.27,0:21:35.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Quando saremo in cinque, andiamoci anche noi!{Cora}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.44,0:21:37.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nella Grand Line!{Cora}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.44,0:21:38.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sì!{angy}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.44,0:21:39.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Andiamoci!{angy}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.69,0:21:44.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Uomini! C'è stata un'interruzione, ma il vero combattimento comincia ora!{Cora}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.87,0:21:46.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ci prenderemo quella nave!{angy}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.54,0:21:47.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,–Sì!\N– Sì!{angy}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.66,0:21:52.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Vecchio, se mi sbarazzo di loro, \Nposso smettere di fare lo sguattero?{angy}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.62,0:21:54.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Fa' come vuoi.{Cora}
